step.action:
Write retro artifact to {reports_dir}/retro-{{sprint_name | slugify}}.md in {{document_language}}:

      # Retrospective — {{sprint_name}} — {{date}}

      ## Sprint Summary
      - Completion: {{done_count}}/{{total_count}} tickets ({{completion_pct}}%)
      - In Progress carried forward: {{in_progress_count}}
      - Abandoned / returned to backlog: {{abandoned_count}}

      ## Tickets Done
      {{done tickets as list with ID and title}}

      ## Tickets Carried Forward
      {{in_progress and todo tickets with notes}}

      ## Went Well
      {{went_well as bullet list}}

      ## To Improve
      {{to_improve as bullet list}}

      ## Action Items
      {{action_items as numbered list, or "None"}}

Write sprint plan artifact to {sprints_dir}/plan-{{next_sprint_name | slugify}}.md in {{document_language}}:

      # Sprint Plan — {{next_sprint_name}} — {{date}}

      ## Capacity
      {{capacity}}

      ## Sprint Scope ({{confirmed_sprint_scope | count}} tickets)
      {{confirmed_sprint_scope as table: ID | Title | Assignee | Points | Priority}}

      ## Dependencies and Risks
      {{list any dependencies or risks flagged during planning}}

      ## Goals
      {{3 bullet goals for the sprint — derived from the ticket themes}}

step.output:
[SPRINT] ✅ COMPLETE
{{if retro: "├─ Retro: {reports_dir}/retro-{{sprint_name | slugify}}.md"}}
{{if planning: "├─ Plan: {sprints_dir}/plan-{{next_sprint_name | slugify}}.md"}}
└─ PM sync: {{pm_tool is configured ? "✓ updated" : "skipped (no PM configured)"}}
